<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-79-0784 </DOCNO><TEXT>This paper traces the history and development of U.S. appraisals of severeaccident risk. The elements and basis of the U.S. Severe Accident Policyand Implementation Program are laid out. Requirements of new reactorapplications and existing plant assessments are described. Regulatorychanges in process or soon to come are described.</TEXT></DOC>